column5: and they sure are biting.  I'll be going for one very last kick in the can in about 30 minutes, but I figured I'd post some pics from two nights ago.  The guys were successful last night as well, beautiful fat 17-19 inchers to boot, and I scored my season high 4 lb to live to see another day     apparently i know where the 10-12 pound monstrosities can be had (Where it stays open 'till Dec 31), but its a farish drive and its really really cold out
Sounds like you've struck gold Congrats on your season high Kwan   Beauty for sure!!! Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice Kwan..you're kicking butt out there. My suggestion...take the long drive and fish for the monsters.
do they close tonight or last night????
Zone 17 will close Nov 15 for Walleye
those are some nice looking fish, well done. If I liked the taste of fish I would be quite envious!
